## Title: LibCodex-1.0-RealmConnections
## Notes: Bundled seed data for LibCodex-1.0 / RealmConnections (Mainline / Retail flavor). LoadOnDemand: LibCodex-1.0 auto-loads this on first :Get() miss against the RealmConnections module. Maps connection group IDs to their member realm IDs (post-merge groupings). Pairs with LibCodex-1.0-Realms.
